3MWF/ref=sr_1_2?ie=UTF8&qid=1368675867&sr=8-2&keywords=strange+cargo+hinterland|publisher=Amazon|accessdate=16 May 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Strange Cargo Discography at Discogs|url=http://www.discogs.com/artist/Strange+Cargo|publisher=Discogs|accessdate=16 May 2013}}</ref>\n*Labels: N-GRAM Recordings\n|}\n\n===With Torch Song===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!| Year\n! style=\"width:250px;\"| Album\n|-\n| 1984\n| ''[[Wish Thing]]''\n*Labels: [[I.R.S. Records]]\n|-\n| 1986\n| ''Ecstasy''\n*Labels: Y II Records\n|-\n| 1987\n| ''Exhibit A''\n*Labels: I.R.S.\n|-\n| 1995\n| ''Toward the Unknown Region''\n*Labels: N-GRAM Recordings\n|}\nDNV 2012\n\n==Production and songwriting credits==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\" width=\"160\"| Title\n!scope=\"col\"| Year\n!scope=\"col\"| Artist(s)\n!scope=\"col\" width=\"180\"| Album\n!scope=\"col\"| Credit(s)\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"24 Hours\"\n|rowspan=\"1\"| 1990\n|rowspan=\"1\"| [[Betty Boo]]\n|rowspan=\"1\"| ''[[Boomania]]''\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Don't Wanna Know 'Bout Evil\"\n|rowspan=\"10\"| 1993\n|rowspan=\"10\"| [[Beth Orton]]\n|rowspan=\"10\"| ''[[Superpinkymandy]]''\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Faith Will Carry\"\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Yesterday's Gone\"\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[She Cries Your Name]]\"\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"When You Wake\"\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Roll the Dice\"\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"City Blue\"\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"The Prisoner\"\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Where Do You Go\"\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Release Me\"\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Turning Ground\"\n|rowspan=\"9\"| 1995\n|rowspan=\"9\"| [[Caroline Lavelle]]\n|rowspan=\"9\"| ''Spirit''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[The Moorlough Shore|Moorlough Shore]]\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Dream of Picasso\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Forget the Few\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Lagan Love\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[A Case of You]]\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Waiting For 