|rowspan=\"2\"| ''[[The Next Best Thing]]''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Time Stood Still\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Runaway Lover\"\n|rowspan=\"3\"| ''[[Music (Madonna album)|Music]]''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Amazing\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Gone\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[Pure Shores]]\"\n|rowspan=\"4\"|  [[All Saints (group)|All Saints]]\n|rowspan=\"4\"| ''[[Saints & Sinners (All Saints album)|Saints & Sinners]]''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Dreams\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[Black Coffee (All Saints song)|Black Coffee]]\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Surrender\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Making Out\"\n|rowspan=\"1\"| 2001\n|rowspan=\"1\"| [[No Doubt]]\n|rowspan=\"1\"| ''[[Rock Steady (album)|Rock Steady]]''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[Thinking About Tomorrow]]\"\n|rowspan=\"3\"| 2002\n|rowspan=\"1\"| Beth Orton\n|rowspan=\"1\"| ''[[Daybreaker (Beth Orton album)|Daybreaker]]''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[Electrical Storm (song)|Electrical Storm]]\"\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[U2]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| ''[[The Best of 1990\u20132000]]''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[The Hands That Built America]]\" <small>(Theme from '[[Gangs of New York]]')</small>\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Sweet Song\"\n|rowspan=\"2\"| 2003\n|rowspan=\"1\"| Blur\n|rowspan=\"1\"| ''[[Think Tank (Blur album)|Think Tank]]''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[Feel Good Time]]\"\n|rowspan=\"1\"| [[Pink (singer)|Pink]]\n|rowspan=\"1\"| ''[[Charlie's Angels: Full Throttle]]''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[Dice (Finley Quaye song)|Dice]]\"\n|rowspan=\"1\"| 2004\n|rowspan=\"1\"| [[Finley Quaye]]\n|rowspan=\"1\"| ''Much More Than Much Love''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[Louise (The Human League song)|Louise]]\"\n|rowspan=\"2\"| 2006\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[Robbie Williams]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| ''[[Rudebox]]''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Summertime\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[To Kill You with a Kiss|I'd Love to Kill You]]\"\n|rowspan=\"13\"| 2010\n|rowspan=\"12\"| [[Katie Melua]]\n|rowspan=\"12\"| ''[[The House (Katie Melua album)|The House]]''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[The Flood (Katie Melua song)|The Flood]]\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[A Happy Place]]\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"A Moment of Madness\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Red Balloons\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Tiny Alien\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"No Fear of Heights\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"The One I Love Is Gone\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Plague of Love\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"God on the Drums, Devil on the Bass\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Twisted\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"The House\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Unbroken\"\n|rowspan=\"1\"| [[Nadine Coyle]]\n|rowspan=\"1\"| ''[[Insatiable (album)|Insatiable]]''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[Gang Bang (song)|Gang Bang]]\"\n|rowspan=\"7\"| 2012\n|rowspan=\"6\"| Madonna\n|rowspan=\"6\"| ''[[MDNA (album)|MDNA]]''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Some Girls\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"I'm a Sinner\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Love Spent\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[Masterpiece (Madonna song)|Masterpiece]]\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Falling Free\"\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[Don't Wake Me Up (song)|Don't Wake Me Up]]\"\n|rowspan=\"1\"| [[Chris Brown]]\n|rowspan=\"1\"| ''[[Fortune (Chris Brown album)|Fortune]]''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[Alien (Britney Spears song)|Alien]]\"\n|rowspan=\"1\"| 2013\n|rowspan=\"1\"| [[Britney Spears]]\n|rowspan=\"1\"| ''[[Britney Jean]]''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"[[There Must Be More to Life Than This]]\"\n|rowspan=\"1\"| 2014\n|rowspan=\"1\"| [[Queen (band)|Queen]] and [[Michael Jackson]]\n|rowspan=\"1\"| ''[[Queen Forever]]''\n| \n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"After All\"\n|rowspan=\"2\"| 2018\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[All Saints (group)|All Saints]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| ''[[Testament (album)|Testament]]''\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Testament in Motion\"\n|\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n\n===Awards===\n* [[Grammy Award for Best Pop Vocal Album]] \u2014 ''[[Ray of Light]]''<ref name=\"grammy\">{{cite web|url=https://www.grammy.com/grammys/artists/william-orbit|title=William Orbit - The Recording Academy|website=GRAMMY.com|publisher=[[The Recording Academy]]|accessdate=August 11, 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Grammy Award for Best Dance Recording]] \u2014 \"[[Ray of Light (song)|Ray of Light]]\"<ref name=\"grammy\"/>\n* [[Grammy Award for Best Song Written for Visual Media]] \u2014 \"[[Beautiful Stranger]]\"<ref name=\"grammy\"/>\n\n===Nominations===\n* [[Golden Globe Award for Best Original Song]] \u2014 \"[[Beautiful Stranger]]\"<ref name=\"IMDb\">{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0649414/awards|title=William Orbit - Awards - IMDb|website=IMDb.com|accessdate=August 11, 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Grammy Award for Album of the Year]] \u2014 ''[[Ray of Light]]''<ref name=\"grammy\"/>\n* [[Grammy Award for Record of the Year]] \u2014 \"[[Ray of Light (song)|Ray of Light]]\"<ref name=\"grammy\"/>\n* [[Grammy Award for Best Pop Instrumental Album]] \u2014 ''[[Pieces in a Modern Style]]''<ref name=\"grammy\"/>\n* [[Grammy Award for Best Pop Collaboration with Vocals]] \u2014 \"[[Feel Good Time]]\"<ref name=\"grammy\"/>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb name|id=0649414|name=William Orbit}}\n* {{Official website|http://www.williamorbit.com}}\n\n{{William Orbit}}\n{{Grammy Award for Best Song Written for Visual Media}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Orbit, William}}\n[[Category:William Orbit| ]]\n[[Category:1956 births]]\n[[Category:Ableton Live users]]\n[[Category:Decca Records artists]]\n[[Category:English composers]]\n[[Category:English record producers]]\n[[Category:Grammy Award winners]]\n[[Category:I.R.S. Records artists]]\n[[Category:People from Shoreditch]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Maverick Records artists]]\n[[Category:Squatters]]\n[[Category:Virgin Records artists]]\n[[Category:Progressive house musicians]]\n[[Category:Downtempo musicians]]\n[[Category:Sanctuary Records artists]]\n", "name_user": "Danno uk", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eT